highlights.text: “Devil in Disguise” by Marino is the highest new entry on Top Songs Singapore at #183.
“你，好不好？ - TVBS連續劇【遺憾拼圖】片尾曲” by Eric Chou has been on Top Songs Singapore the longest, at 3129 days straight.
Jin has the most spots on Top Songs Singapore. “Don’t Say You Love Me” is the highest at #1.
“Which One (feat. Central Cee)” by Drake and Central Cee is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Singapore, up 86 spots at #54.
